முத்த சர்ச்சை VS காதலனை Bigg boss வீட்டுக்குள் அனுப்ப திட்டம் ? : https://youtu.be/cekuWMi_sBA

LEO Success Meet - ரசிகர்களுக்கு செருப்பாய் மாறுவேன் - Vijay Kutty Story : https://youtu.be/D-4PLEiCX8g

Vinoth Seetha - YouTube ல சம்பாதிச்சி வீடு கட்டுவியா ? : https://youtu.be/mD6kd0DZ6XI

Punith Rajkumar மறைவுக்கு 2 வருடம் கழித்து நடந்த…  : https://youtu.be/NkGDn2AP9MU

LEO - கமல் + பகத் நடிக்காததின் காரணம் இதுவே - இத வெளிய சொல்ல மாட்டாங்க : https://youtu.be/JJXpXew427I

மூளையோட Power தாறுமாறா அதிகமாக 7  Brain Techniques : https://youtu.be/MmBDwXVLvwM

Vijay TV - Sandy Master ஐ கூப்பிட்டு 8 மணி நேரம் அவமானபடுத்திய பிரபல நடிகர் : https://youtu.be/H-yMJIwklbY

LEO Review - LCU பஞ்சாயத்தை தாண்டி ஜெயித்து காட்டிய Lokesh  : https://youtu.be/udvbAgFk3fE

LEO - Lokesh கான்பிடென்ஸை பாராட்டித்தள்ளிய Vijay : https://youtu.be/96C_7s8SRc0

Isreal vs Palestine சண்டைக்கு தமிழன் அன்றே சொன்ன ஒரே தீர்வு : https://youtu.be/m1OsbQEpMFk

Vijay TV Jovika  படிப்பை நிறுத்தக்காரணம் bigg boss தான் -கிழித்து தொங்கவிட்ட teacher : https://youtu.be/oDgVppiQoyI

இந்த 6 அறிகுறிகளை விளையாட்டுக்குக்கூட லேசா எடுத்துக்காதீங்க : https://youtu.be/m_NswUt2GxU

LEO படம் பார்த்திட்டு VIJAY சொன்ன வார்த்தை : https://youtu.be/gIHonPNQyS8 

22000 கோடி World Cup மூலம் சம்பாதிக்கும் Bigg boss BCCIக்கு Tax Free ஏன் : https://youtu.be/e2f1d7Q3t-E

5 வருடமாக மறைத்த  ஸ்ரீதேவி மர்மத்தை வெளிச்சத்துக்கு கொண்டு வந்த கணவர் : https://youtu.be/4wStrpfm_6E

Leo Trailer ல 1 கமல் படம் 1 ரஜினி படத்தை ஒளிச்சிவச்சிருக்காரு Lokesh - Vikram Shot : https://youtu.be/FAZt1VJbJt0

LEO - 1000 கோடி கலெக்சன் பண்ணபோறது இப்படி தான் : https://youtu.be/xkoVcT6kQts

Chandrayaan 3  - சத்தமில்லாமல் மீண்டும் வேலையை ஆரம்பித்தது ! SHAPE Mission Begins : https://youtu.be/Lm9W6ArLvvU

கம்மியாக பேசுபவர்களுக்கு இருக்கும் 7 அபார சக்திகள் : https://youtu.be/RDfq8f8IIGE

உண்மையாகவே வாழ்ந்த Chandramukhi க்கு நடந்த பகீர் சம்பவங்கள் : https://youtu.be/syjnMrs9eJc

LEO - 24 வருட Vijay + Kerala கனெக்‌ஷன் & Kerala Collector செய்த Goose bump சம்பவம் : https://youtu.be/Xi7rJmdd33A

தமிழ் விஞ்ஞானிகளுக்கு எதிராக ISRO வில் சூழ்ச்சிவலை பின்னப்படுகிறதா ? : https://youtu.be/dfn7II3l-LY

தமிழ்முறைப்படி Marriage செய்த Ashok Selvan க்கு இவ்வளவு வன்மங்கள் ஏன்? : https://youtu.be/HOKFKz3aOvw

Tamil Pokkisham Vicky & Actress Gautami வாழ்க்கையே ஒரேநாளில் தலை கீழானது : https://youtu.be/EXtxxO05vM8

Chandrayaan 3 - 50 கோடி கொடுத்து பொய் சொல்ல சொன்ன USA நாடகம் அம்பலம்? : https://youtu.be/gIb8gUs8-cU

Shocking - 🇮🇳Pakistan எங்களுக்கு வேண்டாம் இந்தியாவுடன் இணைய விரும்பும் PAK மக்கள் : https://youtu.be/mm0KnG3RSbg

Marimuthu கடைசியாக மனைவியிடம் போனில் சொன்ன அந்த வார்த்தை : https://youtu.be/gmM1Af4-uKs

snippet.title: From Bihar to Big Boss: Manisha Rani's Unveiled Journey
snippet.description:
"Bharti TV के इस पॉडकास्ट में हम जानेंगे कि मनीषा रानी के बिग बॉस से पहले के सफर के बारे में, उनके बचपन से लेकर आज तक की यात्रा में हंसी भी है, भावनाएँ भी हैं, और प्रेरणा तो भर-भर के हैं। तो, इसे enjoy करिए."

"Get ready to ROFL on Bharti TV with the one and only Manisha Rani! 🌟 Join the laughter extravaganza as this Big Boss star brings her regional charm and comedic genius to your screens. 🤣 From side-splitting stories to contagious giggles, this podcast is your weekly prescription for good vibes! Subscribe now and let the emoji party begin! 🎙️😂✨"

snippet.title: कैसे फिर गया Jethalal की इच्छा पर पानी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 9 Nov 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Taarak Mehta felt like eating delicious food today. Jethalal is very excited to eat Jalebi - Fafda. Taarak Mehta comes to Jethalal's house and eats Jalebi Fafda.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 0184
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Samबहादुर - Official Trailer | Vicky Kaushal | Meghna Gulzar | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 01.12.2023
snippet.description:
To the Indian army, to the nation and its people, we present to you a glimpse into the life of India's Greatest Soldier, Sam Manekshaw. 

#SamBahadur Trailer Out Now! 
#Samबहादुर in cinemas 1.12.2023

#SamIsHere 

Samबहादुर is a tribute to Field Marshal Sam HFJ Manekshaw, MC, India's first Field Marshal and a legendary Army General. His career witnessed the shaping of India's geopolitical borders, and his life was marked by significant milestones, from fighting in World War II to being the Chief of Army Staff during the 1971 Indo-Pakistan war, that led to the creation of Bangladesh.
This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

snippet.title: "കരച്ചിൽ കാണാൻ ഇനി ആരും വരേണ്ട"| Renu Sudhi | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #kollamsudhi #flowersstarmagic 

"വിധി ചിലപ്പോഴൊക്കെ ക്രൂരമാണ്".. ഇങ്ങനൊരു അനുഭവത്തിലൂടെ കടന്നുപോയതാണ് രേണു സുധി. രേണുവിന്റെ ഇപ്പോഴുള്ള ജീവിതം നിങ്ങൾ കേൾക്കേണ്ടതാണ്. ഇത്തരം പ്രതിസന്ധിഘട്ടത്തിൽ എങ്ങനെയാണ് രേണുവും, ആ കുടുംബവും ജീവിച്ചു കാണിച്ചുതരുന്നതെന്ന് കേൾക്കാം. ടോക്ക് കാണാം.

Kollam Sudhi was a beloved comedian in the Malayalam entertainment industry who left a lasting impact on his audiences. In this emotional talk, his wife Renu Sudhi speaks candidly about her life with Kollam Sudhi, sharing heartwarming anecdotes and memories. She also touches on the challenges they faced as a family and how they overcame them together. This powerful and touching talk is a tribute to the legacy of Kollam Sudhi, and a must-watch for anyone who loved him. Join us as we celebrate the life and work of this remarkable artist.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.

You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവയെ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഒരു സമ്മേളനമായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

localized.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #kollamsudhi #flowersstarmagic 

"വിധി ചിലപ്പോഴൊക്കെ ക്രൂരമാണ്".. ഇങ്ങനൊരു അനുഭവത്തിലൂടെ കടന്നുപോയതാണ് രേണു സുധി. രേണുവിന്റെ ഇപ്പോഴുള്ള ജീവിതം നിങ്ങൾ കേൾക്കേണ്ടതാണ്. ഇത്തരം പ്രതിസന്ധിഘട്ടത്തിൽ എങ്ങനെയാണ് രേണുവും, ആ കുടുംബവും ജീവിച്ചു കാണിച്ചുതരുന്നതെന്ന് കേൾക്കാം. ടോക്ക് കാണാം.

Kollam Sudhi was a beloved comedian in the Malayalam entertainment industry who left a lasting impact on his audiences. In this emotional talk, his wife Renu Sudhi speaks candidly about her life with Kollam Sudhi, sharing heartwarming anecdotes and memories. She also touches on the challenges they faced as a family and how they overcame them together. This powerful and touching talk is a tribute to the legacy of Kollam Sudhi, and a must-watch for anyone who loved him. Join us as we celebrate the life and work of this remarkable artist.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.

You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവയെ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഒരു സമ്മേളനമായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. snippet.title: Gulab Jamun with Instant Gulab Jamun Mix Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make gulab jamun recipe in tamil. This gulab jamun is made with instant jamun mix. This is very easy to make only requires milk and sugar. The gulab jamun mix can be used in place of mava / khoya. We can use coconut flakes and other nuts to decorate and add texture to these spongy gulab jamuns.
#gulabjamun #gulabjamunrecipe #gulabjamunwithmix 

Friends, please do try this gulab jamun recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Spread the joy cooking during this festival season. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking. 

Wishing everyone a very happy Diwali and enjoy this festival season with homemade sweets.

175g Instant Gulab Jamun mix (1.5 cup)
1/2 cup Milk approx
3 cup Sugar
3 cup Water
few Saffron
Cardamom powder
1/2 tsp Ghee

snippet.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Always remember who you are…

The four nations of the world once lived in harmony, with the Avatar, master of all four elements, keeping peace between them. But everything changed when the Fire Nation attacked and wiped out the Air Nomads, the first step taken by the firebenders towards conquering the world.

AVATAR: THE LAST AIRBENDER, follows a young Air Nomad named Aang, as he reawakens to a world ravaged by war. Together with his newfound friends Sokka and Katara, he embarks on an action-packed quest to take his rightful place as the next AVATAR.

This new live-action reimagining of the award-winning Nickelodeon animated series comes to Netflix in 2024.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

लड़की :- दरद से मर तानी,बड़ी कहर तानी 
चीनी के बोरा लेखा कोरा मे धर तानी
लड़का :- एकही चदर एके खटिया
♥️बिचही लगाई देलु तकिया
काहे फेर के सुतेलु करवटिया
♥️♥️

लड़का :- करेलु दिमाग काहे गरम धरम पत्नी
अंगूरी से चीखे द ना प्यार वाला चटनी
लड़का :- जबे फिलिंग जागे लगल मांगे काहे तले तले 
मल करिहईया ए हो सईया तनी कले कले
लड़का :- घूमी घूमी मारेलु घुलटिया
होखे लागि भउजी हो उलटिया 
काहे फेर के सुतेलु करवटिया....


लड़का :- आशु प्रियांशु प तू अद बद रुसेलु
भीतरी से गच बाड़ू उपरे से गुसेलु
लड़की :- मार जनि मस्का तोहार चस्का ए पिया जान तानी
 नीलकमल एही से ना कहल तोहर मान तानी
लड़का :- मान जा ना धनी तनी बतिया
करे द रंगीन हमार रतिया
काहे फेर के सुतेलु करवटिया
                                       End.

snippet.title: The Truth about Ramayan | Shri Ram | Diwali Special | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
In this video, we delve into the authenticity of the Uttarakand in Valmiki Ramayan, presenting compelling evidence suggesting it may be a later addition. We analyze the concluding chapters of the original text, highlighting how they describe a "happily ever after" scenario in Ram Rajya, which seems inconsistent with the subsequent events in Uttarakand. This provides a strong argument against the inclusion of Uttarakand in the original scripture. Furthermore, the video discusses how the sacred name of "Jai Shree Ram" is being misused today by certain extremist elements to incite violence and hatred. We draw parallels between the misuse of religious chants in various faiths and call for a peaceful reclamation of the name of Lord Ram from those who tarnish it. Join Dhruv Rathee in a thought-provoking exploration of ancient scripture and its relevance in the context of today's world.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3924 | 9 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3924: Sapna Reh Gaya Sapna
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha hears someone calling him out while the Gokuldham villagers joyfully celebrate Garba. Later, Jetha finds that he has been fantasizing about buying the lunar plot and delivering it to Babita all along. Anyway, he finally arrives at the MRP office, and before entering, he contacts Champaklal to wish him well. Jetha also calls Babita and asks her to be present at her house, as he plans to surprise her with his enigmatic gift. Jetha enters the MRP office, but he is taken aback when he sees Popatlal and Chalu Pandey.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3924, 9 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode 3923: Babita Ke Liye Best Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha ultimately tells the inhabitants of Gokuldham about his surprise present for Babita. Jetha dims the lights and produces a lunar-like atmosphere, which surprises everyone. Babita is ecstatic after learning that Jetha has some exciting plans for the actual Moon. Jetha informs Babita that he has purchased a lunar plot for her. Champaklal is taken aback and queries Jetha about it. Other Gokuldham people are skeptical about Jetha's words. Later, Bagha and Nattu Kaka disclose everything to everyone in order to back up Jetha's claim.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3923, 8 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Article 51A(h) in The Constitution Of India 
It shall be the duty of every citizen of India to develop the scientific temper, humanism and the spirit of inquiry and reform.

snippet.title: Mrs Official Teaser | Sanya Malhotra | Nishant Dahiya | Kanwaljit Singh | Arati Kadav
snippet.description:
All set to inspire, move and spark conversations about the challenges & triumphs faced by women globally at the world stage! We are happy to announce our film #Mrs, a captivating story of strength & resilience, will have its World Premiere at #TalinnBlackNightsFilmFestival on 17th November.

The powerful narrative which delves into the life of a married girl who finds her identity amidst navigating her life in kitchen & household chores has also been selected under the Critics’ Pick Competition category at the film festival.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 383
snippet.description:
സൈക്കിൾ റാലിക്ക് പോകാനൊരുങ്ങി ബാലുവച്ചൻ. കൂട്ടിന് രാംകുമാറും ഉണ്ടാകുമോ? റാലിക്ക് പോയ ബാലുവിന്റെ വിവരങ്ങൾ അറിയാൻ കഴിയാതെ വിഷമിക്കുകയാണ് നീലു. ബാലുവിന് എന്ത് സംഭവിച്ചെന്നറിയാൻ കാണുക, 'ഉപ്പും മുളകും'. 

Balu is planning to go for a cycle rally. Will Ramkumar accompany him? Neelu is worried as she haven't heard from Balu from since he left. Keep watching to find out what to Balu.

snippet.title: IND Beat SA: Kohli's Triple Blast, Shoaib Akhtar Shocked! | Aakash Chopra Reaction | World Cup 2023
snippet.description:
India Beats South Africa World Cup 2023 Live Updates: In the match played between India and South Africa in the World Cup 2023, India has defeated South Africa. Batting first, Team India had given a target of 327 runs to South Africa to win. In response to which South African team was out within 100 runs. Kohli played a century for India. Shreyas Iyer played an inning of 77 runs. On the bowling front, Ravindra Jadeja took 5 wickets and Kuldeep took 2 wickets. The entire South African team could score only 83 runs. The 243-run victory, which came on the occasion of Virat Kohli's birthday, was spectacular.

snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal is selling Panipuri on the main road. Suddenly Bagha and Taarak came to eat .Now Stay tuned to know how interstingly Jethalal covered his face and sell them Panipuri. 

Show Name : Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Kush Shah, Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 2575
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#comedy2023 #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch the specially curated series of Pani Puri:
https://studio.youtube.com/playlist/PLSXTaG1fT0cQEuCKKlujcVJPbbmUKJMKD/edit

mr.title: अनारसे | मराठी शॉर्ट फिल्म | @maginajwellery | #Diwali | #भाडिपा

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

🌟 Embark on a Heartwarming Journey with Udaariyaan: Dreams Take Flight! 🌟

Welcome to the captivating world of 'Udaariyaan,' where dreams soar high against the rustic backdrop of a quaint village in Punjab. Join the spirited Sandhu family as they set out on an extraordinary quest to bid adieu to their beloved sarson ke khet and embrace the land of dreams, Canada, fondly known as Kaneda! 🌾🍁🏞️

In this exhilarating tale, fate weaves an unexpected twist, introducing us to the two vibrant sisters, Tejo and Jasmine. Their lives take an enthralling turn when the charming and dashing Fateh walks into their lives, leaving them with heart-pounding emotions and unforeseen challenges. 💓😍🤩

Will these three souls unite their dreams and take flight towards their cherished sapon ki Udaariyaan? Will they overcome the hurdles that destiny throws their way? Experience a rollercoaster of emotions, laughter, and love as you follow their enthralling journey towards making their dreams a reality. 🎢🎭💖

Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? Today’s recipe is Diwali faral shankarpali using 1 kilo maida. It turns out nice, crispy and flaky. Diwali faral is incomplete without shankarpali. We already have seen different recipes if shankarpali. This is full proof recipe the proportion used is just perfect. It is a very easy and simple recipe. You can make it within no time. Besides, I am sharing few tips to make perfect shankarpali. This is a popular Marathi recipe. Also it can be a good tea time snack. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 1 cup Milk
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1 cup Ghee
• 7 cups / 1 kilo Maida
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and add milk and sugar. 
• Heat it up together until sugar is dissolved. 
• When sugar is dissolved and the mixture begins to boil, turn off the gas and add ghee. 
• Melt ghee before measuring. Make sure you don’t use thick ghee. 
• Mix well and base for shankarpali is ready. 
• Transfer the base into the maida and mix in with the help of ladle. 
• Knead the mixture into dough. 
• Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
• Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
• Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
• Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
• Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
• Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
• Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
• If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It won’t dissolve. 
• When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
• You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 382
snippet.description:
എന്തോ കാര്യമായി അന്വേഷിക്കുകയാണ് ലെച്ചു. അന്വേഷിച്ചു ചെന്നപ്പോൾ തനിക്ക് പ്രയോജനമില്ലാത്തതൊന്നും കൈകൊണ്ട് തൊടില്ലെന്നു ബാലു. ലെച്ചുവിന് ഇത്രയും വേണ്ടപ്പെട്ട വസ്തു കൈക്കലാക്കിയതാര്? അറിയുവാൻ മറക്കാതെ കാണുക, 'ഉപ്പും മുളകും'.  

Lechu is searching for something very important. When checked with Balu, he says he wouldn't touch anything that is of no use to him. Who has hidden the thing Lechu is looking for? To find out, watch 'Uppum Mulakum'

snippet.title: La La Heartu Nikkala (Video Song) | Sivaangi • Harsha Vardhan | @mmoriginalstamil #sivaangi  #harsha
snippet.description:
"Lala Heartu Nikkala" is a vibrant and energetic independent song brought to you by MM Originals. This catchy number is composed, sung, and performed by the talented Harsha Vardhan, accompanied by the dynamic singer Sivaangi. Get ready to groove to this fast-paced dance track that's sure to make your heart race and your feet move. Don't miss out on the electrifying music and stunning choreography in this one-of-a-kind musical experience. Subscribe to MM Originals for more exciting content!"

SongTitle : La La Heartu Nikala
Composed by Harsha Vardhan
Vocals - Harsha Vardhan & Sivaangi Krishnakumar
Lyrics - Lavarathan

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 88: एक बुरा सबक 
 -----------------------------------------------------------------
 Malini finds out that Aradhana is her first daughter, and she gets shocked after knowing the truth. She hugs her and promises to give her all the love and affection that she deserves. Aradhana then requests Malini to stop Reyansh and Kimaya's wedding at any cost. Now, stay tuned to know whether  Malini will agree to her requests.

Show Name: Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka
Cast: Shivangi Joshi, Kushal Tandon
Episode: 88
Director: Atif Khan
Producer: Ekta Kapoor

#barsateinmausampyaarka #setindia #बरसातेंमौसमप्यारका #kushaltandon #shivangijoshi 

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

snippet.title: Bardhaman : অসাবধানী TMC MLA, মিডিয়ার মাইক খেয়াল না করেই বলে ফেললেন অন্য এক বিধায়ককে মারার কথা!
snippet.description:
Bardhaman : লঙ্কাগুঁড়োয় লঙ্কাকাণ্ড! অসাবধানী বিধায়কের বেফাঁস মন্তব্য। লঙ্কা গুঁড়ো দিয়ে মেরে ফেলার কথা! TMC রই এক বিধায়ককে মারার কথা আরেক বিধায়কের। মিডিয়ার মাইক খেয়াল না করেই মন্তব্য বিধায়কের।- আউশগ্রামের তৃণমূল বিধায়ক অভেদানন্দ থান্ডারের মন্তব্য। কাটোয়ার বিধায়ক ও জেলা সভাপতি রবীন্দ্রনাথ চট্টোপাধ্যায়ের বিরুদ্ধে মন্তব্য।

#bardhaman #tmc #katwa #banglanews #news18bangla 
n18oc_south-bengal 

News 18 Bangla is an exclusive news channel on YouTube which streams news related to West Bengal, Nation and the World. The channel also has contemporary topic based debate and subject special series which are interesting & informative. Our channel aims to update the viewers with the current news.

বাংলার প্রথম সারির খবরের চ্যানেল নিউজ18 বাংলা ৷ গত বেশ কয়েকবছর ধরে সাফল্যের সঙ্গে খবর পরিবশেন করে আসছে এই চ্যানেল ৷ ব্রেকিং নিউজ থেকে শুরু করে রাজনীতির খবর ৷ জেলা, ক্রাইম, বিনোদন, খেলা, ব্যবসা-বাণিজ্য, প্রাইম টাইম ডিবেট- সব খবর সবার আগে জানতে, দেখতে থাকুন News18 Bangla ৷ চ্যানেলের পাশাপাশি নিউজ18 বাংলার ওয়েবসাইট https://bengali.news18.com/-এ নজর রাখুন ৷
